# Learn Section Content

Browse Greek content organised by topic: conversations, phrases, nouns, verbs, and essentials.

## Route Structure

```
/learn                        Landing page with section cards
/learn/conversations/:tab     Themed dialogues
/learn/phrases/:tab           Common expressions
/learn/nouns                  Noun browser by gender/category
/learn/verbs                  Verb browser by conjugation family
/learn/verbs/:verbId          Full verb conjugation detail
/learn/essentials/:subtab     Building blocks (numbers, colours, etc.)
```

## Landing Page

<route path="/learn">
<purpose>Section hub - visual overview of all learning content areas</purpose>
<file>src/routes/learn/index.tsx</file>
<displays>
- Header: "Learn" with subtitle "Browse Greek content by topic"
- Two groups with section cards:
  - Communication (2 items):
    - Conversations: "Real situations with family and friends"
    - Phrases: "Common expressions and useful phrases"
  - Words (3 items):
    - Nouns: "Objects, people, places — with gender"
    - Verbs: "Actions by conjugation family"
    - Essentials: "Numbers, colours, time, position"
- Each card links to that section's landing/first tab
</displays>
<note>
Cards use colour-coded borders (olive, ocean, honey) matching section themes.
</note>
</route>

## Subsections

See individual content files for detailed documentation:
- `conversations/content.llm` - Themed dialogues
- `phrases/content.llm` - Common expressions
- `essentials/content.llm` - Numbers, colours, time, position, frequency
